manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: NVIDIA AMPERE ARCHITECTURE The Nvidia GeForce RTX 3060 lets you take on the latest games using the power of Ampere—NVIDIA’s 2nd generation RTX architecture, get incredible gaming performance with enhanced Ray Tracing Cores (2nd Generation) and Tensor Cores (3rd Generation). DLSS AI ACCELERATION The NVIDIA DLSS (Deep Learning Super Sampling) is groundbreaking AI rendering technology that increases graphics performance using dedicated Tensor Core AI processors on GeForce RTX GPUs. DLSS taps into the power of a deep learning neural network to boost frame rates and generate beautiful, sharp images for your games. RAY TRACING Ray tracing is the holy grail of gaming graphics, simulating the physical behavior of light to bring real-time, cinematic-quality rendering to even the most visually intense games. SKYLIGHT RGB The iCraft series adopts a new generation of Skylight RGB lighting effects, which can change your computer case to a dazzling light.

iCraft BACKPLATE The iCraft back plate upgrades the RGB lighting effect, the surface is anodized to enhance the texture, and is treated with metal drawing and frosting. The high-strength composite metal material can effectively reinforce the PCB, which is not easy to deform, is not damaged by static electricity and external forces, and the graphics card has a longer life. The multiple cooling holes to reduce the operating temperature of the graphics card. S.I.P POWER SUPPLY SYSTEM The independent S.I.P digital power supply system, with high conversion rate and output voltage, larger power supply current, more precise and powerful control signals to improved power supply and stability of the graphics card. iCraft HYDROMECHANICS FAN The third generation 3X 9CM eleven-blades wide custom design fluid mechanics fan supplemented by a four-phase motor as the power drive, let your graphics card can keep running as quietly as the no-load even when running at full load. LIQUID COOLING HEAT PIPES The iCraft series of graphics cards use the dense fin technology that is only available in high-end products in the industry, and 4 liquid cooling heat pipes with re-flow soldering process, which can significantly enhance the heat transfer efficiency, make your iCraft graphics card has a lower temperature at full load and higher boost frequency.

MULTI-SCREEN WIDER HORIZONS With DPx3/HDMI 2.1 four digital I/O interfaces, support 8K resolution output, multi monitors to enjoy wider audio and video entertainment. GEFORCE EXPERIENCE Capture and share videos, screenshots, and live streams with friends. Keep your drivers up to date and optimize your game settings. GeForce Experience lets you do it all. It’s the essential companion to your GeForce graphics card. GAME READY DRIVERS NVIDIA GeForce Game Ready drivers provide the highest level of performance and the smoothest experience possible, from the moment you start playing. DIRECTX 12 ULTIMATE Developers can now add even more amazing graphics effects to Microsoft Windows-based PC games. GeForce RTX graphics cards deliver advanced DX12 features like ray tracing and variable rate shading, bringing games to life with ultra-realistic visual effects and faster frame rates.

NVIDIA ANSEL Turn your screenshots into art with NVIDIA Ansel, a powerful in-game photo mode that captures 360, HDR, and super-resolution photos. RESIZABLE BAR Resizable BAR is an advanced PCI Express feature that enables the CPU to access the entire GPU frame buffer at once, improving performance in many games. VIRTUAL REALITY The highest performance graphics deliver the smoothest, most immersive VR experiences. NVIDIA G-SYNC Get smooth, tear-free gameplay at refresh rates up to 360 Hz, plus HDR and more. NVIDIA G-SYNC gaming monitors are the ultimate go-to equipment for enthusiast gamers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WELL worth the money
reviews.reviewText: If you're on the fence about it, just buy it.The ONLY con I can find is that I have tried 3 different 3rd party softwares to control the rgb, and none of 'em seem to be able to find the gpu. No complaints about the rgb, but I can't control it. This thing is running great at 1440p, playing genshin impact, honkai star rail, and a few others. Haven't tested it with anything SERIOUSLY demanding yet though. Coupled with a 5700x, for those wondering.

reviews.reviewText: Got exactly as described 12gb 3060 turns out MAXSUN is a great brand and when tested alongside all other variations of 3060 this card ranked 5th out of 48 total cards i gamed and tested the power and temps i was able to game at ultra settings 1080p with no noticeable frame loss, also note that i run 2 more monitors along side this when gaming at 1080, got it to perform at 90-100% utilization and the temp reached 76 once over 30 mins of heavy playing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better Than the 40 Series Equivalent
reviews.reviewText: Incase you didn't know, the more budget-end of the 40 series of GPUs only have about 8gb of VRAM. Which isn't good nowadays, I would much rather have a slower card that can still deliver than a card that is bittlenecked by its VRAM. Less lag spikes and jitter when playing because the system is moving Video Data from your Storage to VRAM (and system RAM if SAM or ReBar is enabled).If your contemplating about buying this or the new 4060 series of GPU, I would buy this or wait until NVidia releases the $399.99 version (16gb VRAM). The 8gb of VRAM is not worthe your money at this point and time.
